summary: An Ordinance accepting a quit claim deed from Fred G. Gidner and Marion E. Gidner, his wife, and Fred Poitras, a bachelor, all of Seattle, Washington, to a certain portion of the North 1/2 of the Northeast 1/4 of the Southeast 1/4 of the Northeast 1/4 of Section 13, Township 25 North, Range 3 East, W. M., all in the City of Seattle, executed on the thirtieth day of December, A. D. 1908.
